title: Future Resource Base Intro
on-arrival: progress = 18
go-to: 19_frb_people

Facilyn: Alright. Simple or elaborate, the key to your Quality of Life Statement is that you have total agreement with everyone involved and that it is meaningfull to you. 

Facilyn: The last area we need to explore is how your future resource base must be to sustain your quality of life. 
